<div>
  <%= f.label :name, 'Template name', class: 'block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700' %>
  <div class="mt-1">
    <%= f.text_field :name, class: 'appearance-none block w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-indigo-500 sm:text-sm' %>
  </div>
</div>

<div>
  <%= f.label :subject, 'Subject', class: 'block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700' %>
  <div class="mt-1">
    <%= f.text_field :subject, class: 'appearance-none block w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-indigo-500 sm:text-sm' %>
  </div>
</div>

<div>
  <%= f.label :body, 'Body', class: 'block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700' %>
  <div class="mt-1">
    <%= f.text_area :body, rows: 20, class: 'appearance-none block w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-indigo-500 sm:text-sm' %>
  </div>
</div>

<div>
  <p class="mb-6">
    You can use <a href="https://shopify.github.io/liquid/basics/introduction/" class="font-medium text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-500">Liquid</a> template syntax in both the subject and body of the template.
    For example, to insert the recipient's name, use <span class="font-mono font-semibold">{{ recipient }}</span>. The following variables are available for you to use:
  </p>
  <div class="flex flex-col">
    <div class="-my-2 overflow-x-auto sm:-mx-6 lg:-mx-8">
      <div class="py-2 align-middle inline-block min-w-full sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="shadow overflow-hidden border-b border-gray-200 sm:rounded-lg">
          <table class="min-w-full divide-y divide-gray-200">
            <thead class="bg-gray-50">
              <tr>
                <th scope="col" class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">
                  Variable
                </th>
                <th scope="col" class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">
                  Description
                </th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr class="bg-white">
                <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">
                  <span class="font-mono font-medium">corporation</span>
                </td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm text-gray-500">
                  The corporation name.
                </td>
              </tr>

              <tr class="bg-white">
                <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">
                  <span class="font-mono font-medium">recipient</span>
                </td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm text-gray-500">
                  The character name of the recipient.
                </td>
              </tr>

              <tr class="bg-white">
                <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">
                  <span class="font-mono font-medium">sender</span>
                </td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm text-gray-500">
                  The character name of the sender.
                </td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
